@startuml State Diagram - Payment Lifecycle
!define TITLE State Diagram - Payment Lifecycle
title TITLE

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #FFE8CC
    BorderColor #FF6600
}

[*] --> Pending: User initiates payment

Pending --> Processing: Payment request sent\nto gateway

Processing --> Completed: Transaction successful
Processing --> Failed: Card declined\nInvalid card\nInsufficient funds

Failed --> Pending: User retries

Completed --> Refunded: Refund requested\n(cancellation/dispute)

Refunded --> [*]

Completed --> [*]

Failed --> [*]

note right of Pending
    Payment created
    Awaiting user confirmation
end note

note right of Processing
    Communication with
    payment gateway (Stripe/PayPal)
    Tokenization done
end note

note right of Completed
    Payment successful
    Transaction ID received
    Funds captured
    Receipt generated
end note

note right of Failed
    Payment declined
    Error details logged
    User notified
    Can retry
end note

note right of Refunded
    Refund initiated
    Processing refund request
    Amount reversed to card
end note

@enduml